channel.description:
[u][b]Pics are from the old site, some were taken by the ex.owner "Sea" mopar profile: DragonicDS, I'll explain what happened in armscape's story after everything.
HD does work and there is old runescape music in the client, I'm sure this is webclient ready. [/b][/u] Onto the pics:
old home: [img]http://i1192.photobucket.com/albums/aa338/DraconicDS/Home-ArmScape-1.png[/img] New home:

Slayer:(max amount assigned is 200) The messages: (i know it's buggy, I can't seem to fully change it back to duradel) [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o1GWPPUVlIU[/youtube]
Now time for the slayer dungeon(all slayer tasks are synchronized with the tower and with the dungeon) I was bored so I went on my mod account(this one was used for investigating people, because I was usally lied to about them doing something) [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/2yvl5w5.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/35kto2s.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/2jcvkw1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/10woggh.png[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/qowxw4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/2csff2w.png[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/34r6ec8.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2eyccx5.png[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/2ms3bqq.png[/img] NOTE: I didn't add the correct hp to some of the monsters in the slayercave. So you'll have to do that, if I make a v2 they will have correct hp. Summoning does work to an extent, hunter does too. The farming is off of painzone, in v2 it will be totally different. Client: small link: http://uppit.com/ia8h7zzc24b6/armscape_client.zip Source: small link: http://up.ht/olvzI1 original: http://uppit.com/4w0u6e3k89iv/armscape_source2.zip ======================================================================================= [b]Credits: 80% painzone 10% DragonicDS (for pics, and sort of because I have to give this guy credits) 10% me.[/b] ======================================================================================= [u][b]Story of armscape part I:(The beggining):[/b][/u] I was originally hired by DragonicDS/ zest as a moderator, I was then promoted to admin and hoster after and incident pertaining with an ass and the ex.hoster. He was stripped of his rank and I became the hoster/admin. If you want further details about the incident pm me. [u][b]Part II:(The middle where everything changed for the better):[/b][/u] After about a month of hosting, DragonicDS was pressuring me to do this that and the next thing, I eventually snapped and Told him off, this resulted in me doing the only rational thing at the time, by banning him and taking the source for mine, I coded it and fixed exactly what he did wrong. In all there was about 52 errors I had to fix from him, I also had to completely redo slayer because of the glitches that used to result from assignment. [u][b]Part III: (The end): [/b][/u] The last 2 months when I was hosting with was extremely annoying, I had 3 ddosers, 1 per week, I had kid's glitching, I had constant asking for staff (extremely annoying), I had kids glitching my ban system, my forums went from everyone being active to absolutely no one online, and lastly like most people, I got tired of hosting this.
[u][b]Part IIII the sequel: [/b][/u] After shutting down armscape, my friend repo/zest and I kept in contact, I forgot to mention that he was there for 100% the entire armscape sega. Anyways the second version is in development, hopefully you will make up your own sega over the armscape base. Our old stats: 50/60 registered users ingame, 30 active on forums, and about 30-40 were on daily. Note: all saved games have been deleted for the user's safety. [u][b]Virus scan: (The auto restarter is a .exe, might bring up suspicion, so here's the scan: )[/b][/u] [u][b]Source:[/b][/u] http://www.virustotal.com/file-scan/report.html?id=c1259a6bf39381550b0f6a280c5ed45953715a8bdcb7fd885c5212aaf86a8781-1318203581
[b]Big note:[/b] If you have connection problems, I'm not going to help, you should learn to portfoward. [b]Another note:[/b] Source doesn't need ip changed in it, it's only the client. [b]Another Big Note:[/b] I'm not helping with any problem, you should learn to solve them yourself, this is not a spoon feeding community. [b]Lastly have fun with it, if there is a source that leeches this (releasing a source without giving credits), then I have full authority to get a mod to lock, be warned you will be flammed for leeching. Have fun, I'll do more shit to it in v2.[/b]
- Judostar1
